nx.description: The shared object has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has partial RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In partial RELRO, the non-PLT part of the GOT section is read only but .got.plt is still writeable. Use the option -z,relro,-z,now to enable full RELRO.

rpath.description: The shared object does not have run-time search path or RPATH set.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

Coinsbit  is a cryptocurrency exchange with which cryptocurrency trading becomes convenient, profitable and safe for you. If you need comfortable trading, go through instant registration using the KYC system in the Coinsbit application and start trading cryptocurrency today, earning on your investments.
 Trading cryptocurrencies with us is convenient! 

BTC, ETH, XRP, LTC, BCH, EOS, TRX, BNB, stable coins (USDT, USDC, TUSD, PAX, DAI), XLM, DASH, XTZ, ETC, ZEC, ADA, ATOM, MIOTA, DOGE, VET, QTUM

Bitcoin BTC, Tether USDT, Ethereum, Litecoin, Ripple, Bitcoin Cash, Binance Coin, EOS, Tron, Stellar, Tezos, Ethereum ETHClassic, Zcash, TrueUSD, Paxos Standard, USD Coin, Cardano, Cosmos, IOTA, NEO, Dogecoin, VeChain, ChainLink QTUM, 0x, REP, LEO, HT, CRO, ZB, BAT, MKR

✓  Buying and Selling Bitcoin : You can easily buy and sell
Bitcoins directly from your Coinsbit account without leaving the mobile application.

✓  Web and Mobile Devices  - You can open your Bitcoin wallet and fully manage it, both via WEB and on mobile devices, and enjoy access to your crypto assets:  Bitcoin  ,  Ethereum ,  XRP ,  Gram ,  Litecoin ,  Monero ,  USDT  and others anytime.

✓  Choosing Coinsbit   as your cryptocurrency exchange , you get a number of functions that make our company unique, and  trading  with us - the most profitable and comfortable .

Our application has a number of advantages over analogues that can be appreciated both by a novice who has just entered the field of crypto trading and an experienced trader who is already well versed in how cryptocurrency exchanges work - regardless of experience, you can make sure that we are out of competition.
 
 About   Bitcoin :

 Bitcoin is a digital currency blockchain , used for the safe and instant transfer of funds anywhere in the world. Like other products or
property, the value of bitcoins is determined by the price of buying and selling on the open market. There are many ways to earn bitcoins - for example:  Bitcoin mining, Bitcoin games or Bitcoin trading.

 Coinsbit will give you the following benefits: 

• Bitcoin (BTC), Litecoin (LTC), Ethereum (ETH), USDT - support for the main coins that are traded on exchanges. Find out the  course of bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies and start trading, choosing the one that is most convenient for you.

• Trading with Coinsbit will be 100% safe - the web application security screen (WAF) detects and blocks hacking attempts, allowing our users to trade without risks - your trade is reliably protected from fraud.

•  - just a few steps that will separate
you from the start of trading - enter your data, create a deposit, place
warrant, and start using Coinsbit.

• Online Technical Support. 24 hours a day you can contact the employee of our application - they will immediately answer all your questions in seven different languages.

•  Simple and convenient interface  - we use a one-page application to make it more comfortable for our customers to use Coinsbit without bothering themselves with a long search for information.

The exchange, which is always with you. Our Coinsbit app allows you to trade cryptocurrency from anywhere in the world. You do not need to have a computer with you to conclude a transaction - everything happens right on your smartphone.

Combining the convenience, security and quality of our service, we have created the best cryptocurrency exchange, the use of which will make your trading on the cryptocurrency rate more convenient and enjoyable than that of competitors - you will not want to trade anywhere except Coinsbit. Convenient charts, an intuitive order system and a classic interface will allow you to successfully join the trade from the first minutes.

Coinsbit - a cryptocurrency exchange that has many positive reviews from satisfied customers.
